<br>
They are part of the group and are good off-tanks (or in some cases, like Calebe's, good primary tanks!).  They do great damage as well.  Why wouldn't a chanter haste a pet?  Why wouldn't a ranger spend the little extra mana giving the pet extra Dex, Agi or ATK buffs?<br>
<br>
I can see why a cleric would hold back an aego or virtue, especially if the pet(s) aren't doing much tanking, but I would at least give the pet Hero/Bulwark.  Why not maximize your groups efficiency and survivability? <p>Benzai Hongkongfooey<br>
